channelDescription:
Free at-home, gym-quality workouts for women looking to get strong, toned & healthy in 5-30 minutes! 

I’m Lauren Fitter, certified personal trainer + prenatal and postnatal exercise specialist, mama to Ava (4) & Audrey (2). 

Whatever your life phase & fitness level, I have an online workout for you! Strength, cardio, interval training, toning, & stretch/mobility workouts + pregnancy & postpartum workouts (including C-section!). You can get in the best shape of your life by working out from home! 

Join our community of strong women, where you’ll feel empowered to accomplish your fitness goals! Subscribe + turn on notifications so you never miss an opportunity to connect + sweat with us! 

Check out my new YouTube Guides to help you get the most out of your workouts! https://laurenfitter.com/programs

comments: I love these workouts. Just finished this one at 35 weeks with 13lbs dumbbells and feeling stronger than ever!!
This felt great at 23 weeks pregnant! My energy/strength looks a lot different these days & 5lb weights were still a great challenge here!💪🩷
That's exactly what I needed. Thank you so much for recording this 💗
Love! I was looking for someone to follow that is calm. Subscribed!

Thanks for this, I love your content.I am 19 weeks and I've been doing this workout 3-4 times a week. Love the core work with the weights overhead. So far no back pain and the bump has made an appearance ❤🙌🏻
